{"tid":418512,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"高登先係正統，方丈肯道歉，大家回歸用新app","createTime":"2017-09-29T15:25:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-30T02:41:40.000Z","uid":34895,"like":7,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4d2de5ad84cc397bceb49fbd946678605885f1d1","tid":418512,"uid":34895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T15:25:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://m.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=6790677\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Fmessage%3D6790677&d=KxpvLRsqdxPhq3FEbq8kmviMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=a1c1bd0c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=6790677</a><br />\n【負荆請罪】全新高登app下週封測　希望大家滿意<br />\n<br />\nBack選單留名<br />\n<br />\n林祖舜(Joe) 3日<br />\n是咁的，呢一年唔少會員因手機app體驗不佳而少上高登，我必須承認整件事係我嘅過失  ，一直有好多熱心會員提供好多優秀嘅建議，只怪我對討論區app經驗不足，未能好好運用會員建議持續改善討論區營運。 <br />\n<br />\n為咗彌補問題，呢一年我哋一直都努力改善後台運作，亦留意多咗對高登不離不棄嘅會員寶貴嘅意見  。我哋亦聯絡咗之前寫HKGz嘅織菊防Gay巴打合作，希望呢隻app嘅面世可以令高登一眾會員感受到我哋嘅誠意。 <br />\n<br />\n新版討論區iOS與Android app完成在即，我們決定於下星期舉行封測，封測分兩個部分，包括公開招募及邀請活躍會員參與： <br />\n<br />\n1. PM邀請活躍會員及曾經對官方app給予意見的會員參與封測。 <br />\n2. 以此post公開招募，如閣下有興趣參與封測，請PM至「高登公關」（會員ID：586349）提供下列資料，我們將盡量安排所有報名會員參加。 <br />\n- iOS用戶：請提供閣下的Apple ID、iPhone型號及iOS版本，我們將提交予Apple作申請封測之用。 <br />\n- Android用戶：請提供閣下的手機型號及Android系統版本做紀錄，我們將直接提供程式apk下載網址作手動安裝。 <br />\n<br />\n兩個邀請程序現在經已展開，希望各位踴躍參加，謝謝。  <br />\n<br />\n開左個post成肚氣，連登好多小學雞"},{"pid":"2b4e014f539ff0e65a9d5214585932696d721da6","tid":418512,"uid":25644,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T15:27:46.000Z","msg":"有早洩，不了"},{"pid":"d08a98725f7c13f72d3d9afc8b76bef5c171be01","tid":418512,"uid":34895,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T15:29:48.000Z","msg":"Sor 講漏左，<br />\n只歡迎心智成熟嘅巴絲打回歸"},{"pid":"733b3dfc1acd57d15d466daf9b8ccf42ed418dcf","tid":418512,"uid":144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T15:33:35.000Z","msg":"冇錢就出黎認低威 不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b528ae594c457d4a3f3511ea19f2ef75b7f192a","tid":418512,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T15:35:49.000Z","msg":"扮死狗<img src=\"http://www.2000fun.com/static/image/smiley/default/titter.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.2000fun.com%2Fstatic%2Fimage%2Fsmiley%2Fdefault%2Ftitter.gif&h=00baf0b2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0d09ebd279fbe7a5b350495fcc41e46e9df4d2fd","tid":418512,"uid":151013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T02:29:12.000Z","msg":"不了"},{"pid":"2088498466a73bbe8a5e9827257f01c5b7d11da8","tid":418512,"uid":36451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T02:37:52.000Z","msg":"返你老母"},{"pid":"a1cd9444dcbebed14e6f759dedac78a7c33123b0","tid":418512,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T02:41:40.000Z","msg":"返iProA紅登? 不了"}]}